name: Alone Together 3
description: An exploration of home, community, and connectedness during an isolating time, by San Francisco paper sculpture artist Zai Divecha. ⫸ This video features physical artwork and practical effects only. ⫸ 10% of first sales will be donated to The Anti Police-Terror Project, a Black-led coalition in Northern California that seeks to build a replicable and sustainable model to eradicate police terror in communities of color. ⫸ MP4, 2000x2000 px, 2021, edition of 10.
